────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Sandbox

    Mode:    contained

    Allowed: read-only ops + write_file & edit_file (with confirmation), run_command (with confirmation)
    Blocked: apply_patch without confirmation, raw shell beyond cwd

    Toggle with: --sandbox=<read-only|contained|unrestricted>
                 or env AGIWORKFORCE_SANDBOX=<mode>
                 or /sandbox <mode> inline
    Enforced by: agiworkforce-sandbox-policy

  Esc to close
